Ireene Wicker https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ireene_Wicker 0 Ireene Wicker (November 24, 1905 – November 17, 1987) was an American singer and actress, best known to young radio listeners in the 1930s and 1940s as “The Singing Lady”, which was the title of her radio program.:305 She added the second 'e' in her first name on the advice of an astrologer.
